            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: left top 3px;
            background-size: 15px;
        } </style> <section class="we-planned bg-vh-2"> <div class="container-fluid"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-7 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center mt-4 mt-md-0"> <h1 class="fs-2">Vaidam's Editorial Policy</h1> <p>Vaidam Health is a trustworthy and number-one healthcare assistance platform providing health and medical travel information to a global audience. Our aim is to give our users relevant information so they can make the best decisions for their health.</p> <h2 class="fs-4 mt-4">Our Medical Content:</h2> <ul class="list-w-circle"> <li>Have guidelines to generate content with a proper framework</li> <li>Easily understandable and knowledgeable</li> <li>Free from plagiarism and AI-generated content</li> <li>Involve facts and statistics</li> <li>Involve authentic resources for references</li> <li>Maintains the highest ethical and editorial standards</li> </ul> <h2 class="fs-4 mt-3">Vaidam Health: A <span class="theam-color">NABH</span> Certified Platform</h2> <p>We are one of the best healthcare assistance platforms connecting patients with top-notch doctors and hospitals worldwide. Our major goal is to provide a hassle-free experience to patients during their medical journey. We have a network in 15+ countries, and we have served more than 25000 patients worldwide.</p> <h2 class="fs-4 mt-4">How We Work?</h2> <ul class="list-w-circle"> <li>Create a list of top doctors and hospitals from different countries.</li> <li>Provide content for different procedures, their costs, hospital stay, right doctor, success rate, factors affecting cost, etc.</li> <li>Information about diseases, illnesses, and procedures is provided via long-form articles and blogs.</li> <li>Create successful patient stories on the website and YouTube.</li> <li>Educate patients by publishing creatives related to procedures and diseases on Social Media platforms like Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter, Facebook, and Youtube.</li> </ul> <h2 class="fs-4 mt-4">How is Our Content Unique?</h2> <ul class="list-w-circle"> <li>Team of trained and knowledgeable content writers from relevant backgrounds.</li> <li>Writers create well-researched content in the form of articles and blogs.</li> <li>Articles are internally linked with relevant topics.</li> <li>Subheads are used to explain topics so that users can understand them easily.</li> <li>Error-free data and user-friendly content.</li> <li>Focus on proper flow and tone of content to target appropriate audiences.</li> <li>Add relevant images, videos, and tables to the article.</li> <li>Review of content by respective authorities or qualified medical professionals.</li> <li>After all the reviews, the author publishes the content on the website.</li> </ul> <h2 class="fs-4 mt-4">Key Values of Our Content</h2> <ul class="list-w-circle"> <li>Simple language</li> <li>Consistent tone</li> <li>Verified information</li> <li>Avoid monotonousness</li> <li>Proper references</li> <li>Specific content</li> </ul> <h3 class="fs-4 mt-4">For Doctors and Hospitals Profile</h3> <p>We ensure that the information in the doctor's and hospital's profiles, such as experience, city name, designation, fees, specialization, visiting hours, address, etc., is updated on time.</p> <h3 class="fs-4 mt-4">For Blogs</h3> <p>Our aim is to provide informative content on our website related to healthcare topics. The articles and blogs are plagiarism-free and are not copied from any other website. We do not provide information about all medical conditions as we focus on major medical departments such as Neurosurgery, Cardiac Surgery, Orthopedic and Joint Replacement Surgery, etc.</p> <h3 class="fs-4 mt-4">For Procedure’s Cost</h3> <p>The procedure’s cost provided on our website is a rough estimate that can vary depending on several factors such as the country chosen, hospital’s location, doctor chosen, city chosen, pre and post-treatment care, etc. Our team can also help you find the right cost as per your requirements.</p> <h3 class="fs-4 mt-4">*Disclaimer*</h3> <em>We put our best effort into writing error-free content for our website. However, any typo, error, or missing/incorrect/non-updated information on the website can occur, and it would be helpful if you let us know at <a href="mailto:hello@vaidam.com">hello@vaidam.com</a>.<br>The content on our website is only for informational purposes, and it is recommended not to consider the information as a doctor’s recommendation.</em> <p class="mt-5">If you have any questions or suggestions, feel free to contact us. You can also join our social media platforms:</p> <p class="fs-5">Follow us</p> <div class="d-flex gap-3 justify-content-start"> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHh2QDCBr0IxT67L_uyr5IQ/playlists" title="YouTube" target="_blank"> <img title="YouTube" class="social-icon" src="https://www.vaidam.com/assets/v2/static_page/images/yt-icon.webp" width="42" height="42" loading="lazy" alt="YouTube"> </a> <a title="LinkedIn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/vaidam-health" target="_blank"> <img title="LinkedIn" class="social-icon" src="https://www.vaidam.com/assets/v2/static_page/images/linkedIn-icon.webp" width="42" height="42" loading="lazy" alt="LinkedIn"> </a> <a title="Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/vaidamhealth" target="_blank"> <img title="Facebook" class="social-icon" src="https://www.vaidam.com/assets/v2/static_page/images/fb-icon.webp" width="42" height="42" loading="lazy" alt="Facebook"> </a> <a title="Instagram" href="https://www.instagram.com/vaidamhealth/" target="_blank"> <img title="Instagram" class="social-icon" src="https://www.vaidam.com/assets/v2/static_page/images/insta-icon.webp" width="42" height="42" loading="lazy" alt="Instagram"> </a> </div> </div> <div class="col-1"></div> <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4 lh-1 position-relative"> <div class="sticy-box sticky-lg-top sticky-lg-top p-3 bg-light rounded-3"> <p class="fs-3 mb-1">Got questions or feedback?</p> <p>Reach us and we’ll gladly answer.</p> <a href="https://www.vaidam.com/lp/consult-online" class="btn btn-danger px-5 mt-3">CONTACT US</a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> </div> </div> </div> 
